  "body": "# Problem\n\nWhen I recover the app or create a new account I receive several pop-ups (Beta alert, Notification settings, Device detected). Likely in the next release a draweer will also come up if I'm on a mobile network.\n\nWhen I go to device pairing, focus goes to the name input field for the device, my keyboard comes up and obtrudes the confirm button of the Beta alert. I'm stuck as I can't complete the Device pairing as the modal obtrudes this screen and I can't get rid of the modal because the keyboard obtrudes the modal.\n\n# Implementation\nWhen a modal is in view, focus should not be on an underlying (main) screen.\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\n\n\n# Notes\n\nRandom notes to keep in mind while implementing it. Mostly about related issues and future plans and thoughts.\n\n# Future Steps\n\nSteps which should be taken after this issue has been resolved.",
